  "detailed_description": "<h1>SUPPORT US!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/64c446e5f95e95ba57580d14ab23ff7c.poster.avif?t=1751284835\" width=600 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/64c446e5f95e95ba57580d14ab23ff7c.webm?t=1751284835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/64c446e5f95e95ba57580d14ab23ff7c.mp4?t=1751284835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exciting Secret Agent Adventures</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Island Ops will take you on a thrilling adventure as you slip into the shoes of a secret agent, codename Blade. Infiltrate a secret military base and discover a litany of mysteries contained within.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/5a7d2ed0cfc39e53b5746fadb2ace668.poster.avif?t=1751284835\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/5a7d2ed0cfc39e53b5746fadb2ace668.webm?t=1751284835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/5a7d2ed0cfc39e53b5746fadb2ace668.mp4?t=1751284835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strategic Infiltration and Reconnaissance Missions</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your intelligence and cunning to infiltrate the secret facility. But that is just the beginning. Pay careful attention to every detail to create a dynamic plan. Explore every aspect of the facility to determine who the real threat is. Your life depends on it! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/01efd6f30e30ed099774e491178623fd.poster.avif?t=1751284835\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/01efd6f30e30ed099774e491178623fd.webm?t=1751284835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/01efd6f30e30ed099774e491178623fd.mp4?t=1751284835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Filled with Unexpected Surprises</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll encounter something unexpected in the research facility and trace the traces of extraordinary experiments. In this mysterious world, the importance of your decisions and actions is significant. You must plan each step carefully and use your creativity to solve unexpected situations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/c5ec81ff431035a229d43ed24c936d09.poster.avif?t=1751284835\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/c5ec81ff431035a229d43ed24c936d09.webm?t=1751284835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/c5ec81ff431035a229d43ed24c936d09.mp4?t=1751284835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Action-Packed Obstacles and Challenges</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Agent Blade must overcome all obstacles inside the facility with his mind and weapon. By using your skills, you'll need to strategically navigate a path to defeat enemies and successfully complete your mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/4a6be5bad04794775a5824fabd20150c.poster.avif?t=1751284835\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/4a6be5bad04794775a5824fabd20150c.webm?t=1751284835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/4a6be5bad04794775a5824fabd20150c.mp4?t=1751284835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Save the World, Stop the Outbreak!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The secret experiment in the research facility has turned into a mutation outbreak. Blade is taking action to destroy these dangerous mutations. The world's salvation depends on your decisions and fighting strength.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/5a577e27b0f9dec1c729dcf1462864c6.poster.avif?t=1751284835\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/5a577e27b0f9dec1c729dcf1462864c6.webm?t=1751284835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/5a577e27b0f9dec1c729dcf1462864c6.mp4?t=1751284835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >An Experience of Fun and Adrenaline</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Island Ops\" will pull you into a story full of suspense, action, and mystery. Guide your character, use your intelligence and skills to save the world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/2c1577cf0aee6fbdab620529854a3a28.poster.avif?t=1751284835\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/2c1577cf0aee6fbdab620529854a3a28.webm?t=1751284835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/2c1577cf0aee6fbdab620529854a3a28.mp4?t=1751284835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game appeals to any player who wants to explore its mysterious world and embark on an action-packed adventure. With its captivating story, challenging puzzles, and action-packed scenes, \"Island Ops\" offers an unforgettable gaming experience!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exciting Secret Agent Adventures</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Island Ops will take you on a thrilling adventure as you slip into the shoes of a secret agent, codename Blade. Infiltrate a secret military base and discover a litany of mysteries contained within.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/5a7d2ed0cfc39e53b5746fadb2ace668.poster.avif?t=1751284835\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/5a7d2ed0cfc39e53b5746fadb2ace668.webm?t=1751284835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/5a7d2ed0cfc39e53b5746fadb2ace668.mp4?t=1751284835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strategic Infiltration and Reconnaissance Missions</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your intelligence and cunning to infiltrate the secret facility. But that is just the beginning. Pay careful attention to every detail to create a dynamic plan. Explore every aspect of the facility to determine who the real threat is. Your life depends on it! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/01efd6f30e30ed099774e491178623fd.poster.avif?t=1751284835\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/01efd6f30e30ed099774e491178623fd.webm?t=1751284835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648150/extras/01efd6f30e30ed099774e491178623fd.mp4?t=1751284835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></vide